            company&#x27;s pivot from a blockchain-first marketplace to an AI-native solutions factory, market
            activity around the token quieted while product, positioning, and the build workflow were rebuilt
            end-to-end. <strong>That rebuild is now shipping</strong>, and the token moves with it.
          </p>
