            $BWS-settled usage, programmatic buybacks and burns, and staking benefits</strong> — not a promise of
            specific amounts, ratios, or timing. Execution is deliberately discretionary so markets can&#x27;t
            front-run it. What we <em>do</em> commit to is on-chain transparency: every buyback and burn is
            observable on-chain after it happens, and headline totals are reported on an ongoing basis.
